						<summary>

						<p>Pāṇḍya, Māṟavarman •••Pāṇḍya, 8+3rd year = c. 12th-13th Century.</p>						

						<p>This records a gift of land as tax-free <hi rend="italic">tiruviḍaiyāṭṭam</hi> to the temple of Guṇagaṇābh araṇa-Viṇṇagar-emberumāṉ at Kumbaṉūr <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Guṇagaṇābharaṇa-nallūr in Veṇbuḷa-nāḍu by a Kaṉṉināṭṭaraiyaṉ after purchasing it from the ūrār of the village.</p>						

						<p>[Published in <hi rend="italic">Virudhunagar District Inscriptions</hi>, No. 148/2005.]</p>						

