<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> kOmāṟa<hi rend="grantha">panma</hi>rāṉa <hi rend="grantha">tribhu</hi>vaṉaccakkaravattikaḷ <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> pāṇṭiya tEvarkku yāṇṭu Eṭṭāvatiṉ Etir mūṉṟāvatu veṇpuḷa nāṭṭuc ceṅkāṭṭirukkai kumpaṉūrāṉa kuṇa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>kaṇāparaṇanallūr kuṇakaṇāparaṇa viṇṇakar Emperumāṉu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ṉ caruṇāṭaṉāṉa kaṉṉināṭṭaraiyaṉēṉ Ivvūr Ūrar pakkal peṟṟup peruṅkuḷattu tuyal pilāṟṟukku vaṭakku nālāṅkaṇṇāṟṟu
<lb n="3"/>paṉṉiraṇṭāñ cey <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ntaḻamañ cāṇkōlāl kuḻinūṟum Ik <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kkiṇaṟum Ūrāṟku vilaittiraviyaṅ kuṭuttu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> Iṟai kuḻi <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> Iṟaiyili tiruviṭaiyāṭṭamāy ca<hi rend="grantha">ntrā</hi>tittavaṟai
